version 3.0.3
2013-03-07 

1. Implementation by nxweb. 
2. Only kyotocabinet library is necessary, libevent is dropped.
3. Change finally executable file name to "adfslite".
4. Modify configure.ac. Add check for "kclangc.h", "libkyotocabinet".

